{"tid":2118003,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有個HD，拎個Top up Degree定讀第二科轉行好？","createTime":"2020-07-21T08:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T17:40:49.000Z","uid":91427,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9febf291540c5e52be6ffbe454fe209e43e89bb0","tid":2118003,"uid":91427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:04:21.000Z","msg":"自己之前HD Media科畢業，係一間細公司做左幾年野，而家27歲<br />\n做耐左覺得無咩方向，自己又無話想係呢行發展，<br />\n好似睇唔到出路咁，好迷惘<br />\n<br />\n知自己唔想係到做一世，<br />\n但無一技之長，出去搵工唔知做也好<br />\n搵工好多都要Degree<br />\n自己一路都想有返張沙紙<br />\n所以今年想再讀返書<br />\n其實幾年前都有諗過，不過驚頭驚尾無實行<br />\n<br />\n第一樣諗既係Top up Degree，1年讀完<br />\n讀完我諗無話有咩特別優勢<br />\n叫做有返個Degree，<br />\n之後應該會搵工做住<br />\n然後疊埋心水考ACO個D<br />\n<br />\n第二樣係讀第二科轉行 <br />\n我想報個IT hd/asso，叫做專D<br />\n讀既話會想認真讀再上UGC，但畢業都31歲<br />\n會擔心出黎搵唔到野做<br />\n<br />\n想聽下大家意見，唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50b10f0a082a2ef2371527e083675bbd82f70e5","tid":2118003,"uid":104804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:07:43.000Z","msg":"做youtuber 全職讀一年topup<br />\n之後再搵工"},{"pid":"32d3ee674c5484a3afedc278b3cf3e2d9614004d","tid":2118003,"uid":333199,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"讀HD NURSE 做RN<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b611ad5ee8cb8dac36c90bb29b0cc836a9331e","tid":2118003,"uid":35605,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"第一 本身有hd 再讀top up degree竟然為考aco係咩玩法？定三十歲人仲想叫人為興趣讀書？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二 係香港讀IT仲要係HD/asso 又係咩玩法？<br />\n字裡行間離不開top up/hd/asso<br />\n屌 你話你唔係Pr 我都唔撚信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ace2fc2a0b8de6b26e7c808ef29a03674a3ad9","tid":2118003,"uid":205272,"like":0,"disli